name: CreateDecorator
description: CreateDecorator is fired when a BiomeDecorator is created. This event is fired whenever a BiomeDecorator is created in DeferredBiomeDecorator#fireCreateEventAndReplace(BiomeGenBase). originalBiomeDecorator contains the original BiomeDecorator that would be used in vanilla. newBiomeDecorator contains the new BiomeDecoration to be used by Minecraft. This event is not Cancelable . This event does not have a result. Event.HasResult This event is fired on the MinecraftForge#TERRAIN_GEN_BUS .
